Maxima followed Carnation & the others. Remaining silent. Such foolishness in 
the ranks. The only time she recalled this happening was when the Leaders 
were not in control. 

Her clear blue optics were focusing on the others. But still awaiting a reply 
from Carnation. Who was this supposed Decepticon?

But.. at current, she would watch these troops. If they got far too out of 
hand, she would put them in their places. 

--part1_a1.3649a1a7.2bb63447_boundary
